items.name: DJI Mini 2
items.description: With intuitive and advanced features housed in a portable design, DJI Mini 2 gives you complete freedom wherever you are and how you want to create. Whether you're recording on a deserted beach or trying to capture the details of a family get-together, DJI Mini 2 handles it with ease.

items.name: DJI Tello Boost Combo
items.description: Operating the Tello is child's play! Just pull out the phone and thanks to the intuitive controls you can fly whenever you want. Feel like you are in the cockpit of an airplane with a breathtaking first-person view. Tello is Compatible with VR headsets. The Tello drone is based on DJI technology. It uses the best components that guarantee stable flights.
